\SE[57]I see... I see...? So the study of Eros is also
advancing.... \SE[32]It's a different approach from the
academy....

\SE[12]Indeed, it's important to always have a broad
perspective. There are as many possibilities as there are
people who have tried...
\SE[22]I'm your lover, you know~. \.Can I come in?

\SE[57]...Oops, I was frozen by your cuteness. \SE[16]Oh,
it's no problem. Please come in.

\SE[5]...Oh, were you studying? \!\SE[29]I don't want to
disturb you. \.Should I come back later?

\SE[0]No, don't worry about it. \SE[0]I just need a
little more time, so relax in the room.
\SE[22]Oh, I see. Okay, take your time and relax.

\SE[12]I see... \SE[33]Compared to the cold regions of
Cordin, the high self-sufficiency of food makes it easier to
stabilize the economy due to geographical factors...

\SE[3]Cordin is trying to resolve that difference through
military force. \SE[33]There is inevitability in the
tendencies of each country... I see... I see...?

\SE[2]...In other words, the interpretation of history can
differ between the Ulysian perspective and the Cordin
perspective, even for the same events. \SE[3]Each side is
promoting their own understanding to benefit their own
country...

\SE[33]...I see. \.To obtain accurate information, a
multifaceted perspective is necessary.... \!\SE[2]Relying
solely on school knowledge is still lacking in
viewpoints....

\SE[2] (Somehow, I'm looking at the mirror... \SE[3] I
wonder what I'm thinking...)

\SE[12] (I want you to look at me without looking in the
mirror... \!\SE[13] It's enough for me to be reflected in
your eyes...)

\SE[2]If you think about it normally, Ulysia has the
advantage... \!\SE[3]But ten years ago, a revolution
occurred. \.The king was assassinated, and his son took the
throne...?

\SE[47]...This isn't in their textbooks over there. \.It
seems that after a long battle with illness, a generational
change took place.... \!\SE[3]I see... Other countries are
looking at it more objectively.

\SE[2]And thanks to the strong leadership of the current
king, Cordin has experienced significant growth...
\SE[3]That is the foundation of that country...

\SE[58] (Right now, Laura is sleeping in my bed...?
\!\SE[57] No, this is bad. My head is filled with lewd
fantasies since earlier, and I can't concentrate at all.)

\SE[59] (I need to find a way to relieve myself somehow,
otherwise I won't be able to think straight with all these

\SE[6]Ah, um... No, that's not it. \SE[21]There's something

\SE[85]Me...? Hmm. I don't think I'll be of much help
though...

\SE[0]No. That's not true. This is something only you can

\SE[12] (...What is this creature? It's incredibly cute...
\. I want to hold it... \!\SE[13] I want to ravish it and
